Docker & Kubernetes Senior SRE Guide
Practical Study and Lab Reference (Basic → Advanced)

This document provides a complete learning path for Docker and Kubernetes from the perspective of a Senior Site Reliability Engineer (SRE).

It is designed to:

prepare for Senior SRE interviews

serve as a hands-on lab guide

understand real production infrastructure

Topics progress from foundations → advanced reliability engineering concepts.

1. What a Senior SRE Must Know About Containers

A Senior Site Reliability Engineer must understand:

containerization

orchestration

scaling

observability

production reliability

